<item>
            <title>[LU-16516] remove duplicate convert_facet2label() function</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16516</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;test-framework.sh::convert_facet2label()&lt;/tt&gt; function is redundant with &lt;tt&gt;facet_svc()&lt;/tt&gt; and has a longer name, so it will be removed and callers replaced with &lt;tt&gt;facet_svc()&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a few callers that pass &quot;&lt;tt&gt;ost&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; as the facet name, which is replaced by &quot;&lt;tt&gt;ost1&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; internally, but they can also pass &lt;tt&gt;ost1&lt;/tt&gt; directly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
